20dumped%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cap%20off%20a%20volatile%20week.%20Oil%20continued%20to%20churn%20higher%20as%20Donald%20Trump's%20reassurances%20failed%20to%20calm%20nerves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20latest%20announcement%20that%20he%20would%20put%20off%20bombing%20Iran's%20energy%20infrastructure%20did%20little%20to%20soothe%20market%20jitters%20on%20Friday.%20Major%20indexes%20capped%20off%20their%20worst%20week%20of%20the%20war%20so%20far%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrent%20crude%3C%2Fa%3E%20rose%20settled%20at%20nearly%20%24113%20per%20barrel%2C%20the%20highest%20level%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstant%20flip-flopping%20and%20headline%20fatigue%20is%20starting%20to%20undermine%20the%20%5BTrump%5D%20put%20efficacy%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Ftrump-stocks-oil-price-iran-markets-war-wall-street-sell-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBarclays%20analysts%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20ahead%20of%20the%20day's%20heaviest%20selling.%20%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20the%20war%20goes%20on%2C%20and%20the%20longer%20the%20oil%20shock%2C%20the%20more%20severe%20the%20stagflationary%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20particularly%20grim%20milestones%20that%20summarize%20the%20stock%20market's%20rough%20week%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bc3c606-0e09-49f3-a058-7aa2329b7bb4%5C%22%3E1.%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20Dow%20enter%20correction%20territory%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20major%20indexes%20are%20halfway%20to%20a%20bear%20market%20as%20of%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fdow_jones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDow%3C%2Fa%3E%20teetered%20for%20most%20of%20the%20day%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20defined%20as%20a%20more-than-10%25%20drawdown%20from%20a%20recent%20peak%20%E2%80%94%2