2The%20attack%20came%20after%20the%20Yemeni%20group%20had%20threatened%20to%20join%20the%20regional%20war%20if%20its%20ally%2C%20Tehran%20continued%20to%20be%20attacked%20or%20if%20more%20countries%20joined%20the%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyemens-houthis-join-iran-war-after-threats-launch-1st-missile-on-israel-11278295%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyemens-houthis-join-iran-war-after-threats-launch-1st-missile-on-israel-11278295%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyemens-houthis-join-iran-war-after-threats-launch-1st-missile-on-israel-11278295%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RCB%20vs%20SRH%3A%20Five%20players%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774686600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129849026%2Cimgsize-1261374.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Frcb-vs-srh-ipl-2026-5-players-to-watch-out-for-in-todays-clash%2Farticleshow%2F129848856.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20face%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%20a%20high-pressure%20opening%20match.%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Phil%20Salt%20will%20aim%20for%20strong%20starts%20for%20RCB.%20Abhishek%20Sharma%20and%20Travis%20Head%20bring%20attacking%20intent%20for%20SRH.%20Ishan%20Kishan%20leads%20SRH%20with%20added%20responsibility.%20This%20contest%20promises%20a%20run-fest%20with%20individual%20brilliance%20expected%20to%20decide%20the%20outcome.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Informed'%20traders%20on%20Polymarket%20netted%20%24143%20million%20in%20'anomalous'%20profit%20since%202024%2C%20researchers%20find%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22polymarket%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6e76e8e5f53c45ea2d016%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BInformed%26quot%3B%20Polymarket%20users%20made%20%24143%20million%20since%202024%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20analyzed%20most%20of%20Polymarket's%20trades%20between%202024%20and%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20co-author%20told%20BI%20he%20hoped%20the%20analysis%20would%20inform%20prediction-market%20regulation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20a%20new%20Polymarket%20account%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3Bricosuave666%26quot%3B%20began%20betting%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20on%20specific%20questions%20regarding%20Israeli%20military%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gamble%20paid%20off.%20When%20Israel%20struck%20Iran%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20June%2013%2C%20ricosuave666%20pocketed%20roughly%20%24155%2C000%20before%20going%20dormant%20for%20seven%20months.%20The%20account%20resurfaced%20in%20January%202026%20to%20place%20new%20wagers%20%E2%80%94%20before%20analysts%20flagged%20its%20activity%20and%20it%20was%20promptly%20deleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERicosuave666's%20moves%20were%20among%20more%20than%20210%2C000%20suspicious%20Polymarket%20trades%20analyzed%20by%20researchers%20at%20Columbia%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Haifa.%20The%20trades%20netted%20%24143%20million%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Binformed%26quot%3B%20traders%20who%20made%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D6426778%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhose%20findings%20were%20published%20this%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20suspicious%20trade%20made%20by%20ricosuave666%20was%20only%20the%203%2C662nd-most%20unusual%20trade%20in%20the%20data%2C%20authors%20Joshua%20Mitts%20and%20Moran%20Ofir%20wrote.%20They%20said%20ricosuave666's%20gains%20closely%20matched%20ill-gotten%20gains%20attributed%20to%20a%20person%20charged%20by%20Israeli%20authorities%20with%20using%20military%20secrets%20to%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20which%20analyzed%20most%20of%20Polymarket's%20trades%20between%202024%20and%202026%2C%20is%20the%20first%20to%20provide%20an%20estimate%20for%20the%20total%20amount%20won%20by%20suspicious%20accounts%2C%20whose%20activities%20are%20often%20flagged%20by%20market%20observers%20and%20traders%20on%20X%20and%20Discord%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20used%20five%20criteria%20relating%20to%20trade%20timing%20and%20amounts%20wagered%20to%20screen%20for%20accounts%20that%20made%20big%2C%20bullish%20bets%20shortly%20before%20news%20broke%2C%20though%20they%20acknowledged%20that%20their%20methods%20could%20have%20been%20over-inclusive%20or%20under-inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20any%20reason%20to%20think%20that%20the%20unobserved%20relationships%20are%20cutting%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitts%2C%20a%20Columbia%20Law%20School%20professor%20who%20has%20previously%20written%20about%20potential%20insider%20trading%20in%20equities%20markets%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20and%20Ofir%20generally%20used%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Binformed%26quot%3B%20trading%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Binsider%26quot%3B%20trading%20because%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20trades%20they%20flagged%20took%20place%20in%20markets%20where%20too%20many%20people%20influence%20the%20outcome%20for%20it%20to%20be%20rigged%2C%20like%20those%20related%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%202024%20election.%20%26quot%3BInformed%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20broader%20term%20that%20encompasses%20trades%20made%20by%20smart%20bettors%20as%20well%20as%20those%20with%20unfair%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20said%20the%20election%20bets%20were%20included%20with%20other%20%26quot%3Banomalous%26quot%3B%20bets%20because%20the%20authors%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20accused%20of%20massaging%20their%20methodology%20to%20get%20a%20particular%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20regulatory%20attention.%20We%20see%20this%20as%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df304fa1-b2aa-44a3-87e3-ba4b9625c99e%5C%22%3ENo%20proof%20of%20insider%20trading%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20said%20it's%20possible%20that%20they%20flagged%20profitable%20trades%20that%20were%20part%20of%20a%20hedging%20strategy%20and%20offset%20by%20a%20loss%20in%20another%20wallet%20controlled%20by%20the%20same%20user.%20Still%2C%20they%20characterized%20the%20volume%20of%20suspicious%20trades%20they%20identified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bconservative%20lower-bound%20estimate%20of%20anomalous%20profits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarry%20Crane%2C%20a%20Rutgers%20statistics%20professor%20who%20has%20written%20about%20prediction%20markets%20and%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study%2C%20questioned%20its%20methodology.%20While%20the%20study%20ranked%20over%20210%2C000%20bets%20based%20on%20how%20unusual%20the%20bets%20were%20for%20the%20traders%20who%20made%20them%20and%20for%20the%20markets%20where%20they%20were%20made%2C%20the%20ranking%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Bsuspiciousness%26quot%3B%20was%20heavily%20skewed%20by%20profitability%2C%20rather%20than%20what%20ordinary%20people%20would%20consider%20suspicious%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20winning%20bet%20is%20getting%20disproportionately%20more%20weight%20than%20a%20losing%20bet%20of%20the%20exact%20same%20type%2C%26quot%3B%20Crane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%2020%20most%20suspicious%20trades%20identified%20in%20the%20paper%2C%20accounting%20for%20about%20%2416%20million%20of%20the%20%24143%20million%20in%20profits%20reaped%20by%20flagged%20accounts%2C%20related%20to%20the%202024%20election%20results.%20Others%20related%20to%20Federal%20Reserve%20decisions%20and%20sports%20match-ups%2C%20where%20manipulation%20is%20theoretically%20possible%20or%20insider%20information%20theoretically%20could%20have%20leaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitts%20said%20the%20plan%20was%20eventually%20to%20publish%20all%20the%20data%20used%20for%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrediction%20markets%20have%20outpaced%20the%20legal%20frameworks%20designed%20to%20govern%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BOur%20paper%20aims%20to%20provide%20the%20empirical%20grounding%20and%20legal%20analysis%20necessary%20to%20close%20that%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22537256c5-21cd-49f5-b9cf-3a365febd6f4%5C%22%3EPolymarket%20changed%20its%20policy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20have%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20initially%20as%20academic%20experiments%20and%20later%20as%20a%20tool%20popular%20with%20members%20of%20the%20so-called%20rationalist%20community.%20The%20general%20idea%20is%20highly%20accurate%20guesses%20about%20the%20future%20can%20emerge%20from%20a%20group%20of%20non-experts%20who%20put%20their%20money%20where%20their%20mouths%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advocates%20for%20prediction%20markets%20see%20insiders%20cashing%20in%20as%20a%20feature%2C%20not%20a%20bug.%20Shayne%20Coplan%2C%20Polymarket's%20founder%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20that%20Polymarket%20%26quot%3Bcreates%20this%20financial%20incentive%20to%20divulge%20information%20to%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20260320997513%2Fen%2FPolymarket-Publishes-Enhanced-Market-Integrity-Rules-Across-Its-DeFi-Platform-and-CFTC-Regulated-U.S.-Exchange%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20banning%20trades%20by%20people%20with%20%26quot%3Bstolen%20confidential%20information%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Billegal%20tips%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20trades%20by%20people%20who%20can%20influence%20the%20outcomes%20of%20events%20they're%20betting%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20company%20will%20enforce%20the%20prohibition%20when%20it%20doesn't%20know%20who%20its%20users%20are.%20While%20the%20company%20has%20a%20regulated%20US%20subsidiary%2C%20that%20entity%20processes%20less%20than%2010%25%20of%20the%20volume%20of%20trades%20as%20the%20offshore%20exchange%2C%20which%20doesn't%20collect%20users'%20names%20or%20other%20identifying%20information%20beyond%20an%20email%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20reply%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20announced%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20it%20is%20seeking%20fines%20from%20two%20users%20who%20broke%20its%20rules%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-bans-fines-users-youtube-streamer-california-politician-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20editor%20for%20MrBeast%20who%20placed%20bets%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20what%20words%20would%20be%20said%20on%20shows%20before%20they%20were%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20grew%20slowly%20for%20years.%20In%202025%2C%20Kalshi%20grew%20rapidly%20after%20it%20began%20offering%20Americans%20the%20chance%20to%20bet%20on%20sports%20in%20a%20way%20it%20calls%20more%20fair%20than%20sportsbooks.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquitting-polymarket-kalshi-prediction-markets-problem-gambling-addiction-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProblem%20gambling%20experts%20are%20concerned%20that%20prediction%20markets%20pose%20similar%20risks%20to%20sportsbooks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20and%20several%20states%20have%20sued%20Kalshi%20and%20other%20prediction%20markets%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20amount%20to%20unlicensed%20casinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20a%20federal%20regulator%2C%20fined%20Polymarket%20in%202022%20and%20generally%20prevented%20prediction%20markets%20from%20offering%20many%20contracts%20until%20Trump%20took%20office%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Selig%2C%20a%20Trump%20appointee%20who%20took%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20regulator%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20a%20vociferous%20advocate%20for%20such%20markets%2C%20and%20criticized%20the%20states%20for%20their%20crackdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Know%20more%3F%20Reach%20Jack%20Newsham%20via%20email%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajnewsham%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejnewsham%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E)%20or%20via%20Signal%20(%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B13149711627%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%2B1-314-971-1627%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E).%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20here's%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eour%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-informed-insider-trades-study-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774686361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6ea04f573a637a75670e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-informed-insider-trades-study-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20study%20analyzed%20most%20Polymarket's%20trades%20between%202024%20and%202026.%20It's%20the%20first%20to%20estimate%20the%20total%20amount%20won%20by%20suspicious%20accounts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnewsham%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-informed-insider-trades-study-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Animal%20Friends%E2%80%99%20to%20hit%20theatres%20in%20early%202027%20now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774686123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129861472%2Cimgsize-110556.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fryan-reynolds-and-jason-momoa-starrer-animal-friends-release-date-shifts-again-to-hit-theatres-in-early-2027-now%2Farticleshow%2F129861472.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129861472.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOriginally%20scheduled%20for%20May%202026%2C%20'Animal%20Friends%2C'%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20film%20starring%20Ryan%20Reynolds%20and%20Jason%20Momoa%2C%20will%20now%20hit%20theaters%20on%20January%2022%2C%202027.%20The%20release%20has%20been%20postponed%20due%20to%20the%20impressive%20cast%2C%20which%20includes%20Aubrey%20Plaza%20and%20Dan%20Levy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Why%20was%20a%20bizman%20present%3F'%3A%20Cong%20questions%20PM%20Modi%20over%20Musk's%20presence%20in%20Trump%20call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774686082000%2C