e%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20documents%20were%20released%20in%20Elon%20Musk's%20lawsuit%20against%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20unredacted%20documents%20show%20text%20messages%20between%20Musk%20and%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20sought%20Zuckerberg's%20support%20to%20bid%20on%20OpenAI%20in%20February%202025%2C%20according%20to%20unsealed%20messages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20asked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20he%20would%20consider%20joining%20him%20in%20bidding%20for%20OpenAI's%20intellectual%20property%20before%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20made%20an%20unsolicited%20offer%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20maker%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202025%2C%20according%20to%20newly%20released%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20unredacted%20documents%20are%20part%20of%20Musk's%20ongoing%20lawsuit%20against%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20CEO%2C%20Sam%20Altman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20provide%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20communication%20between%20Musk%20and%20the%20Meta%20CEO%2C%20who%20have%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vs-mark-zuckerberg-feud-history-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroller%20coaster%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20challenges%20to%20MMA%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20unsealed%20exhibit%2C%20Zuckerberg%20texted%20Musk%20at%2010%3A04%20p.m.%20PT%20on%20February%203%2C%202025%2C%20to%20say%20that%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%2C%20for%20which%20Musk%20was%20the%20de%20facto%20leader%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20progress.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20added%20that%20his%20%26quot%3Bteams%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bon%20alert%20to%20take%20down%20content%20doxxing%20or%20threatening%26quot%3B%20people%20who%20work%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20at%20DOGE%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20know%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20else%20I%20can%20do%20to%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20half%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20Musk%20reacted%20to%20Zuckerberg's%20message%20with%20a%20heart%20emoji%20and%20followed%20up%20with%20a%20question%20about%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20bidding%20on%20the%20OpenAI%20IP%20with%20me%20and%20some%20others%3F%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20common%20term%20for%20intellectual%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWant%20to%20discuss%20live%3F%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20liked%20Zuckerberg's%20message%20and%20texted%20back%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20would%20%26quot%3Bcall%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20the%20planned%20call%20actually%20took%20place.%20A%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20has%20no%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20court%20briefing%20OpenAI%20filed%20on%20August%2021%2C%202025%2C%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bidentified%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20as%20a%20person%20he%20communicated%20with%20regarding%20a%20letter%20of%20intent%20about%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20financing%20arrangements%20or%20investments%26quot%3B%20in%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Zuckerberg%20nor%20Meta%20signed%20the%20LOI%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20added%20in%20the%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20and%20a%20senior%20legal%20counsel%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%202025%2C%20a%20consortium%20of%20investors%2C%20including%20xAI%2C%20led%20by%20Musk%2C%20submitted%20an%20unsolicited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-elon-musk-97-billion-bid-openai-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%2497.4%20billion%20bid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20acquire%20the%20then-nonprofit%20organization%20that%20controls%20OpenAI.%20The%20bid%2C%20submitted%20by%20Musk's%20attorney%20Marc%20Toberoff%2C%20was%20aimed%20at%20blocking%20OpenAI's%20transition%20into%20a%20for-profit%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20promptly%20responded%20to%20the%20bid%20on%20X%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%20thank%20you%20but%20we%20will%20buy%20twitter%20for%20%249.74%20billion%20if%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-elon-musk-and-sam-altman-relationship-feuds-2023-3%23musk-sued-open-ai-again-in-august-2024-this-time-saying-he-was-deceived-into-cofounding-the-company-16%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20sued%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20on%20the%20OpenAI%20board%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20deceived%20into%20investing%20and%20that%20the%20founders%20originally%20approached%20him%20to%20fund%20a%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20developing%20AI%20to%20benefit%20humanity%2C%20but%20that%20it%20was%20now%20focused%20on%20generating%20profit.%20Musk%20contributed%20around%20%2438%20million%20to%20OpenAI%20in%20its%20initial%20years%20but%20is%20now%20seeking%20up%20to%20%24134%20billion%20in%20damages%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20version%20of%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20conversation%20between%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Musk%20on%20December%2013%2C%202024%2C%20Zuckerberg%20told%20Musk%20that%20someone%20had%20%26quot%3Bleaked%26quot%3B%20Meta's%20letter%20to%20the%20California%20Attorney%20General%20in%20support%20of%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-seeks-134-billion-legal-battle-over-open-ai-microsoft-2026-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elawsuit%20against%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWanted%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20heard%20this%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20officially%20completed%20its%20conversion%20from%20a%20nonprofit%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-completes-restructuring-for-profit-signs-new-microsoft-agreement-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor-profit%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202025%2C%20although%20it%20still%20maintains%20a%20nonprofit%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawsuit%20against%20Altman%20and%20OpenAI%20will%20begin%20jury%20selection%20on%20April%2027%20in%20Oakland%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-pitched-mark-zuckerberg-on-bid-for-openai-ip-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774663943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6dac18373a547629c72da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-pitched-mark-zuckerberg-on-bid-for-openai-ip-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20asked%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20if%20he%20would%20consider%20joining%20him%20in%20bidding%20for%20OpenAI's%20IP%2C%20according%20to%20newly%20released%20court%20documents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-pitched-mark-zuckerberg-on-bid-for-openai-ip-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20US%20President%20calls%20it%20%E2%80%98Strait%20of%20Trump%2C%E2%80%99%20then%20says%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a