e%20brakes%20on%20users%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Claude%20website%20is%20seen%20on%20a%20laptop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6deacf573a637a756703d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20has%20adjusted%20usage%20caps%20for%20Claude%20subscribers%20during%20peak%20times.%3Cp%3Eillustration%20by%20Michael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20adjusted%20Claude%20usage%20caps%20during%20peak%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20changes%20show%20that%20the%20AI%20company%20is%20experiencing%20some%20compute%20strain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20saw%20a%20surge%20of%20interest%20after%20the%20Pentagon%20moved%20to%20effectively%20blacklist%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20conquering%20is%20starting%20to%20stretch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-ai-tools-tech-selloff-software-apocalypse-cybersecurity-anthropic-ibm-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Anthropic%20adjusted%20its%20usage%20limits%20for%20Claude%20free%2C%20Pro%2C%20and%20Max%20subscribers.%20While%20weekly%20limits%20don't%20change%2C%20it%20means%20users%20will%20approach%20their%20cap%20more%20quickly%20when%20they%20are%20using%20Claude%20during%20peak%20hours%2C%20which%20Anthropic%20defines%20as%20between%205%20am%20to%2011%20am%20Pacific%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20landed%20a%20lot%20of%20efficiency%20wins%20to%20offset%20this%2C%20but%20~7%25%20of%20users%20will%20hit%20session%20limits%20they%20wouldn't%20have%20before%2C%20particularly%20for%20pro%20tiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Thariq%20Shihipar%2C%20who%20works%20on%20Claude%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20run%20token-intensive%20background%20jobs%2C%20shifting%20them%20to%20off-peak%20hours%2