I%20know%20this%20was%20frustrating%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Anthropic%20official%20wrote%20in%20an%20announcement%20of%20the%20changes.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20continuing%20to%20invest%20in%20scaling%20efficiently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-usage-caps-changes-popularity-anthropic-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There's%20a%20valuable%20leadership%20lesson%20in%20this%20viral%20March%20Madness%20moment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maryland%20basketball%20coach%20yelling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6b48e8e44c01630d31806%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20clip%20of%20University%20of%20Maryland's%20Brenda%20Frese%20passionately%20coaching%20an%20athlete%20went%20viral.%3Cp%3EGrant%20Halverson%2FNCAA%20Photos%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20University%20of%20Maryland%20basketball%20coach's%20intense%20pep%20talk%20with%20a%20player%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20athlete%2C%20Oluchi%20Okananwa%2C%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bforever%20appreciative%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20interaction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20leadership%20lesson%20in%20building%20strong%20relationships%20and%20knowing%20what%20motivates%20your%20team.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-watch-march-madness-college-basketball-2026-v2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echaos%20of%20March%20Madness%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20simple%20leadership%20lesson%3A%20Know%20your%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Brenda%20Frese%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20basketball%20coach%2C%20went%20viral%20after%20cameras%20showed%20her%20shouting%20passionately%20at%20one%20of%20her%20players.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20you%2C%20but%20you%20got%20to%20want%20this%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20junior%20guard%20Oluchi%20Okananwa%2C%20just%20a%20few%20inches%20away%20from%20her%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20interaction%20might%20appear%20abrasive%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sparked%20debate%20online%20about%20whether%20it%20crossed%20a%20line%20%E2%80%94%20Frese's%20message%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20exactly%20what%20Okananwa%20needed%20in%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20to%20be%20coached%20hard%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20she%20does%20with%20me%20every%20single%20day.%20And%20really%20what%20that%20was%2C%20was%20a%20regroup%20moment%20for%20myself%20and%20her%20telling%20me%20she%20believed%20in%20me%2C%20because%20sometimes%20that's%20really%20all%20you%20need%20to%20hear%2C%26quot%3B%20Okananwa%20said%20at%20a%20post-game%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guard%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bforever%20appreciative%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20interaction%2C%20and%20after%20the%20heated%20conversation%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20the%20court%20and%20locked%20in%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoments%20like%20this%20can%20reflect%20a%20deeper%20level%20of%20trust%20between%20a%20coach%20and%20a%20player.%20In%20high-pressure%20situations%2C%20direct%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanged-management-style-new-hire-quit-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemotionally%20charged%20feedback%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20cut%20through%20the%20noise%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20requires%20a%20strong%20relationship%2C%20according%20to%20Frese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post-game%20press%20conference%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFrese%20said%20that%20a%20coach%20needs%20to%20know%20their%20players.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20those%20conversations%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20relationship%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.yahoo.com%2Fwomens-college-basketball%2Farticle%2Fmarylands-oluchi-okananwa-addresses-viral-interaction-with-coach-brenda-frese-in-march-madness-loss-i-love-to-be-coached-hard-211159833.html%3Fguce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAANpB6Sak_QXkiJTEEQcGYAGFvAYmwyChf7ZhInemmb94VO9OItXuMzLNeW161to0ATkeMeumhOUXKEJU3iZN1w_FRl1decQZXnPFhec4RwgNFKwvKNwGUuyV-JjIQXFcgs2AyZvDQqpI_MSBOVmMWnse40OR7YfM6Y3mA_HcAcs8%26_guc_consent_skip%3D1774641685%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Yahoo%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22daaa488c-6e13-46a8-a4bf-8499dc086e01%5C%22%3EKnowing%20your%20players%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20meaningful%20distinction%20between%20tearing%20someone%20down%20and%20delivering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdouble-edged-sword-high-performers-face-at-work-feedback-managers-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirect%2C%20emotionally%20charged%20feedback%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20Frese's%20approach%20pushed%20Okananwa%20while%20also%20showing%20confidence%20in%20her%20ability%20to%20meet%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20have%20to%20at%20times%20have%20those%20tough%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20Frese%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BThe%20best-of-the-best%2C%20the%20elite-of-the-elite%20wanna%20be%20coached%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Quigley%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20strategic%20leadership%20and%20governance%20at%20IMD%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Frese%20likely%20understood%20exactly%20what%20her%20player%20needed%20to%20hear%2C%20and%20that%20delivering%20it%20with%20intensity%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20part%20of%20the%20culture%20of%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20and%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20your%20whole%20being%2C%20your%20whole%20soul%2C%20everything%20you've%20got%2C%20to%20compete%20at%20that%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Quigley%20said.%20%26quot%3BLittle%2C%20teeny%20things%20make%20all%20the%20difference.%20And%20that%20coach%20is%20working%20to%20get%20that%20out%20of%20her%20player.%20She%20knows%20her%20player%20and%20she%20cares.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuigley%2C%20who%20previously%20competed%20internationally%20as%20a%20cyclist%2C%20said%20those%20kinds%20of%20exchanges%20were%20common%20with%20his%20own%20coach.%20He%20added%20that%20while%20that%20specific%20kind%20of%20interaction%20is%20unlikely%20to%20occur%20in%20a%20boardroom%2C%20most%20CEOs%20have%20likely%20had%20similar%20moments%20of%20intensity%20with%20their%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20in%20the%20workplace%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20about%2C%20let's%20say%2C%20it's%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20acquisition%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20yell%20at%20each%20other%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Quigley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuigley%20said%20the%20context%20in%20those%20scenarios%20is%20crucial.%20When%20people%20establish%20strong%20relationships%20and%20understand%20how%20to%20motivate%20their%20direct%20reports%2C%20those%20moments%20of%20feedback%20can%20be%20critical%20in%20helping%20them%20perform%20better%20without%20feeling%20belittling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleadership-lesson-viral-march-madness-moment-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774643633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6b46a8e44c01630d31805%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleadership-lesson-viral-march-madness-moment-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brenda%20Frese's%20courtside%20exchange%20with%20a%20Maryland%20player%20shows%20the%20importance%20of%20knowing%20what%20motivates%20your%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%