ia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnegligent-discharge-former-first-lady-jill-bidens-secret-service-agent-accidentally-shoots-leg-while-on-duty%2Famp_articleshow%2F129854099.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnegligent-discharge-former-first-lady-jill-bidens-secret-service-agent-accidentally-shoots-leg-while-on-duty%2Famp_articleshow%2F129854099.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20kicked%20off%20Biden's%20affordable%20plan%20are%20required%20to%20restart%20payments%20this%20fall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a5b9f5d3e2f1aef369ce8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20will%20soon%20need%20to%20find%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan.%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20is%20sending%20notices%20on%20the%20next%20steps%20to%20student-loan%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeginning%20July%201%2C%20SAVE%20borrowers%20will%20have%2090%20days%20to%20select%20a%20new%20plan%20and%20begin%20payments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20who%20do%20not%20select%20a%20new%20plan%20will%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20to%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%3A%20Get%20off%20SAVE%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pay%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20announced%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20will%20begin%20sending%20notices%20to%20the%207%20million%20borrowers%20enrolled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-get-guidance-next-steps-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailing%20their%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enext%20steps%20for%20repayment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20on%20July%201%2C%20according%20to%20the%20department%2C%20servicers%20will%20notify%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20that%20they%20have%2090%20days%20to%20select%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan%20and%20resume%20making%20payments.%20Borrowers%20who%20do%20not%20select%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan%20will%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan%2C%20and%20loan%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eservicers%20will%20notify%20them%20of%20their%20specific%20enrollment%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2090-day%20period%20provides%20borrowers%20with%20ample%20time%20to%20explore%20repayment%20options%20that%20best%20suit%20their%20needs%20and%20plan%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20borrower%20who%20wishes%20to%20transition%20before%20their%20loan%20servicer%20communicates%20a%20specific%2090-day%20deadline%20may%20contact%20their%20servicer%20at%20any%20time%20to%20enroll%20in%20a%20lawful%20repayment%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Kent%2C%20the%20undersecretary%20of%20education%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20statement%20that%20borrowers%20will%20receive%20further%20guidance%20%26quot%3Bover%20the%20next%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20borrowers%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20confusing%20cycle%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20but%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20policy%20is%20simple%3A%20if%20you%20take%20out%20a%20loan%2C%20you%20must%20pay%20it%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAVE%20was%20created%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20give%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20and%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20loan%20forgiveness.%20The%20plan%20had%20been%20blocked%20since%20the%20summer%20of%202024%20due%20to%20litigation%2C%20and%20borrowers%20on%20it%20have%20not%20been%20required%20to%20make%20monthly%20payments.%20A%20federal%20judge%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-whats-next-for-student-loan-borrowers-trump-settlement-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapproved%20a%20settlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Missouri%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20states%20that%20filed%20the%20litigation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20eliminate%20SAVE%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20allowed%20the%20administration%20to%20eliminate%20SAVE%20and%20move%20borrowers%20to%20new%20plans%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20spending%20legislation%2C%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20repayment%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20borrowing%20caps%2C%20would%20have%20eliminated%20SAVE%20by%202028.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20that%20SAVE%20borrowers%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20enroll%20in%20the%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20is%20less%20generous%20than%20existing%20plans%20and%20allows%20for%20relief%20after%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20loans%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-next-steps-restarting-repayment-trump-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774643219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6e0508e5f53c45ea2cfb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-next-steps-resta