ce%20and%20may%20discipline%20those%20who%20don't%20show%20up%20when%20they're%20supposed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManagers%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20team%20members%20meet%20the%20full-time%20in-office%20requirement%2C%26quot%3B%20Paramount%20said%20in%20a%20separate%20RTO%20FAQ%20document.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20expectations%20aren't%20met%2C%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20discipline%20up%20to%20and%20including%20dismissal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20toolkit%20document%2C%20Paramount%20shared%20specific%20questions%20that%20managers%20can%20ask%20reports%20to%20check%20in%20or%20flag%20noncompliance%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHow's%20it%20going%20coming%20back%20into%20the%20office%20every%20day%3F%20Is%20there%20anything%20you%20need%20or%20anything%20I%20can%20do%20to%20support%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20keeping%20you%20from%20coming%20into%20the%20office%20on%20those%20days%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20toolkit%20document%20also%20said%20that%20bosses%20won't%20initially%20have%20access%20to%20attendance%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20managers%20will%20not%20have%20access%20to%20data%20to%20show%20them%20who%20is%20and%20is%20not%20coming%20into%20the%20office.%20Managers%20will%20eventually%20have%20access%20to%20this%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Paramount%20manager%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20responsibility%20of%20tracking%20where%20employees%20work%20%26quot%3Bseems%20daunting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20hall%20monitor%20on%20top%20of%20all%20the%20work%20we%20already%20have%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20has%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-return-to-office-rto-survey-employees-five-days-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein-person%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20key%20to%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bnext%20gen%20media%20and%20entertainment%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20theme%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-reorg-tech-new-streaming-features-execs-wbd-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20David%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20spoken%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20isn't%20the%20only%20media%20company%20that's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-media-companies-rto-wfh-paramount-nbcu-disney-netflix-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epushed%20for%20in-person%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20most%20of%20its%20rivals%20let%20staffers%20work%20from%20home%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBCUniversal%20implemented%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnbcuniversal-rto-order-four-days-week-memo-paramount-amazon-microsoft-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efour-day-per-week%20RTO%20mandate%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%2C%20and%20Disney%20employees%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20work%20at%20the%20office%20four%20days%20a%20week.%20Employees%20at%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-declines-warner-bros-bid-raise-wbd-paramount-skydance-ellison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhich%20Paramount%20is%20buying%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20commute%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20while%20Netflix%20lets%20staffers%20work%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-return-to-office-rto-remote-work-managers-employees-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774641212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6c20e8e44c01630d318a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2