findia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fis-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-becoming-a-lord-report-says-keir-starmer-considering-peerage-to-shore-up-his-own-position%2Farticleshow%2F129851439.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fis-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-becoming-a-lord-report-says-keir-starmer-considering-peerage-to-shore-up-his-own-position%2Famp_articleshow%2F129851439.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fis-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-becoming-a-lord-report-says-keir-starmer-considering-peerage-to-shore-up-his-own-position%2Famp_articleshow%2F129851439.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20is%20running%20intensive%20AI%20training%20weeks%20to%20get%20employees%20testing%20agents%20and%20coding%20with%20Claude%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6c1af8e44c01630d3189d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20latest%20AI%20push%20at%20Meta%20is%20%26quot%3BAI%20Week%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20employees%20build%20things%20using%20Claude%20and%20other%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStaff%20is%20spinning%20up%20interactive%20vibe%20coding%20guides%2C%20competing%20in%20hackathons%2C%20and%20watching%20demos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2026%20is%20the%20year%20AI%20will%20begin%20to%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20change%20the%20way%20we%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Meta%2C%20there's%20no%20escaping%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20begun%20running%20intensive%20AI%20training%20weeks%20to%20encourage%20staff%20to%20experiment%20more%20with%20AI%20tools%2C%20according%20to%20Meta%20employees%20who%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20and%20public%20LinkedIn%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weeks%20have%20involved%20a%20series%20of%20hackathons%2C%20demos%2C%20and%20other%20projects%20where%20Meta%20staff%20show%20off%20what%20they%20can%20build%20with%20AI%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20job%20title%20or%20seniority.%20Some%20of%20the%20projects%20are%20built%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-anthropic-ai-llama-coding-efficiency-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20company%20has%20adopted%20widely%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20Meta's%20latest%20initiative%20to%20embrace%20AI%20across%20its%20workforce%2C%20which%20has%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-push-employee-goals-tool-adoption-2-026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esetting%20org%20targets%20for%20AI%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reorganizing%20some%20teams%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-native%20%26quot%3Bpods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Similar%20pushes%20are%20taking%20place%20across%20corporate%20America%20as%20companies%20aim%20to%20become%20more%20efficient%20with%20AI.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-ai-adoption-non-technical-software-engineer-performance-review-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20has%20told%20some%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20AI%20use%20will%20be%20considered%20in%20performance%20reviews%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-objectives-software-engineers-developers-boost-productivity-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20has%20told%20software%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20expects%20them%20to%20be%20harnessing%20AI%20to%20save%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20well-known%20that%20this%20is%20a%20priority%20and%20we're%20focused%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20employees%20with%20their%20day-to-day%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20these%20sessions%20have%20been%20given%20names%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BAI%20Transformation%20Week.%26quot%3B%20During%20the%20sessions%2C%20some%20employees%20were%20given%20demos%20on%20how%20agents%20and%20other%20tools%20could%20work%20across%20their%20laptops%20and%20phones%2C%20an%20employee%20who%20attended%20some%20sessions%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20AI%20weeks%20took%20place%20in%20March.%20One%20Meta%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20teams%20held%20their%20own%20AI%20weeks%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20during%20which%20staff%20used%20vibe%20coding%20to%20create%20something%20valuable%20with%20no%20strict%20output%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20hackathon%20during%20Meta's%20AI%20Transformation%20Week%2C%20attendees%20sat%20through%20demos%20of%20its%20own%20internal%20AI%20tools%2C%20Claude%20Code%2C%20and%20others%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Finkedin.com%2Fposts%2Ftbarrondesign_another-day-of-ai-week-at-meta-i-joined-activity-7435021001861517312-_jIc%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAADHUUIEBu9ykWEQA6ZCNi-WBJ4dxkaU6GpY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20an%20employee.%20AI%20agents%20are%20a%20big%20focus%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20having%20employees%20guide%20autonomous%20systems%20that%20can%20handle%20everything%20from%20coding%20to%20compiling%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesign%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20effort.%20One%20Meta%20product%20manager%20touted%20building%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmengxie.me%2Fprojects%2Fplaybook.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ei