0deal%20to%20fund%20DHS%20and%20pay%20TSA%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20TSA%20worker%20pay%20remains%20uncertain%20as%20the%20House%20GOP%20says%20no%20ICE%20funding%20is%20a%20no-go.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20pay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-agents-working-without-pay-how-much-salary-they-make-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETransportation%20Security%20Administration%20employees%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20stalemate%20in%20Congress%20over%20ending%20the%20partial%20shutdown%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20hits%20a%20new%20stumbling%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2026%2F03%2Fmemorandum-for-the-secretary-of-homeland-security-and-the-director-of-the-office-of-management-and-budget%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20on%20Friday%2C%20directs%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20%26quot%3Bto%20use%20funds%20that%20have%20a%20reasonable%20and%20logical%20nexus%20to%20TSA%20operations%20to%20provide%20TSA%20employees%20with%20the%20compensation%20and%20benefits%20that%20would%20have%20accrued%20to%20them%20if%20not%20for%20the%20Democrat-led%20DHS%20shutdown.%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20said%20that%20he%20has%20determined%20that%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20circumstances%20constitute%20an%20emergency%20situation%26quot%3B%20that%20compromises%20the%20country's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Republican%20members%20of%20the%20House's%20Freedom%20Caucus%20are%20signaling%20they%20won't%20move%20forward%20with%20a%20proposal%20to%20fund%20DHS%2C%20potentially%20lengthening%20a%20shutdown%20that%20began%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20Friday%20morning%2C%20the%20Senate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-reaches-deal-fund-tsa-dhs-end-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evoted%20to%20move%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20proposal%20to%20end%20the%20partial%20shutdown%20that's%20currently%20preventing%20TSA%20workers%20from%20getting%20paid.%20The%20Senate-approved%20proposal%20excludes%20funding%20for%20immigration%20operations%20and%20came%20as%20Congress%20prepared%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-workers-could-miss-another-paycheck-partial-government-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edepart%20on%20a%20scheduled%20recess%3C%2Fa%3E%20Friday%20evening.%20For%20that%20legislation%20to%20become%20law%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20TSA%20workers%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20passed%20by%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20the%20Senate%20be%20any%20more%20lazy%20than%20to%20send%20to%20us%20a%20bill%20that%20doesn't%20do%20the%20job%20and%20then%20leave%20town%3F%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Chip%20Roy%2C%20a%20Republican%20from%20Texas%20and%20member%20of%20the%20House%20Freedom%20Caucus%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRepChipRoy%2Fstatus%2F2037570214468911505%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20at%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20going%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20say%20no%20to%20that.%20We're%20going%20to%20send%20back%20a%20bill%20that's%20responsible%20to%20the%20American%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20setback%20in%20a%20partial%20shutdown%20that's%20left%20TSA%20workers%20with%20two%20missing%20paychecks%20and%20American%20travelers%20stuck%20in%20hourslong%20lines%20at%20airports%20across%20the%20country.%20Hundreds%20of%20TSA%20workers%20have%20quit%2C%20and%20thousands%20have%20called%20out%20as%20they%20go%20without%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Freedom%20Caucus%20members%20have%20said%20they%20want%20to%20add%20ICE%20and%20Border%20Patrol%20funding%20back%20into%20a%20spending%20package%2C%20measures%20that%20the%20Senate-passed%20package%20omitted.%20House%20Republicans%20have%20also%20eyed%20a%2060-day%20stopgap%20funding%20measure%2C%20which%20Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F2037581253365412224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdead%20on%20arrival%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%20and%20Republicans%20know%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story%2C%20check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-worker-pay-shutdown-house-stalls-funding-proposal-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774637301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6cf43e99557fb1b08a1de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-worker-pay-shutdown-house-stalls-funding-proposal-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22House%20Republicans%20are%20pushing%20back%20on%20a%20Senate-approved%20proposal%20to%20fund%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20and%20get%20TSA%20workers%20paid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jkaplan%40businessinsider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-worker-pay-shutdown-house-stalls-funding-proposal-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jazz%20Musician%20Chuck%20Redd%20Seeks%20Dismissal%20of%20%E2%80%98Trump%20Kennedy%20Center%E2%80%99%20Lawsuit%20Against%20Him%20Over%20Canceled%20Christmas%20Eve%20Gig%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774637220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236701704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%9CTrump%20Kennedy%20Center%E2%80%9D%20earlier%20this%20month%20followed%20through%20on%20its%20threat%20to%20sue%20acclaimed%20jazz%20musician%20Chuck%20