ens%3A%20a%20return%20to%20grains%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20paired%20with%20microgreens%20that%20can%20be%20grown%20on%20a%20windowsill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496778%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20nostalgia%20driving%20this%20change%2C%20but%20necessity.%20Rising%20childhood%20obesity%2C%20allergies%2C%20and%20attention%20issues%20are%20nudging%20parents%20to%20rethink%20food.%20Nutritionists%20are%20urging%20families%20to%20revive%20traditional%20superfoods%2C%20not%20as%20a%20trend%2C%20but%20as%20everyday%20essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F478326%2Fpalak-arora-millium-millet-startup-ready-to-eat-mixes-ready-to-cook-supporting-local-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20millets%20and%20microgreens%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20hailed%20as%20game-changers%3F%20And%20how%20can%20today%E2%80%99s%20busy%20parents%20weave%20them%20into%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20diets%20without%20mealtime%20battles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMicrogreens%3A%20Tiny%20greens%2C%20big%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20microgreens%20still%20conjure%20images%20of%20fancy%20restaurant%20plates.%20But%20step%20into%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20Indian%20homes%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%